casebody.data:
Tuesday, November 19, 1991

MOTION DOCKET

91-2130. Beekman v. Beekman.

Franklin County, No. 90AP-780. This cause is pending before the court on the filing of a motion for an order directing the Court of Appeals for Franklin County to certify its record and as a claimed appeal as of right from said court. Upon consideration of appellant's motion for stay,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said motion for stay be, and the same is hereby, denied, effective November 15, 1991.
